A monumentally corrupt, monstrously violent totalitarian state always consolidates itself to preside over corruption.In times of unbearable suffering by the vast majority of the people, expect government functionaries to be completely out of touch. The Covid-19 pandemic is utterly ruthless. Humans have always been vulnerable to viruses. But this particular mutant has also exposed the abject vulnerability of human institutions, including the state.
A lot of the power and efficacy that states and governments have always claimed and projected have been exposed as nothing more than woeful sham. Beyond pomp and ceremony, parades and displays, formalities and protocols, the African state in particular has been shown to be all hat.



