Absurd days
One would hope that those deliriously absurd days are firmly behind us. One would be dismayingly wrong. In times of unbearable suffering by the vast majority of the people, expect government functionaries to be completely out of touch, insulting, reckless, utterly and unnecessarily thoughtless. That is the sign of the times.



