The message of the Leviathan is elementary: you are on your own; keep quiet (wear a mask), and stay out of the way (social distance), or contend with teargas, rungus and nyahunyos. 
The government side perfectly equanimous; they are obscenely lavished with government largesse.
Nevertheless, happy new year!
Mr Ng’eno is an advocate of the High Court and a former State House speechwriter; @EricNgeno Cartels consume twice every year what legitimate county governments get in one year. We live at a time of tremendous burgeoning of ministerial clout. According to family members, the deceased was attached to the DP’s security detail for several years. The footbridge was damaged by a trailer carrying an excavator earlier in December 2020. However they made us feel, the men and women in this list elicited different emotions in all of us.